# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Swift Tasks — Environment Variables
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# This file is a template. Run `node setup.js` to copy it to .env
# automatically, then fill in your values below.
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Database (Neon serverless Postgres)
# Go to https://neon.tech, create a project, and copy the connection string here.
DATABASE_URL="postgresql://user:password@ep-xxx.region.aws.neon.tech/dbname?sslmode=require"

# AES-256-GCM encryption key for API key storage (32 bytes = 64 hex chars)
# Generate one with:  openssl rand -hex 32
# Or let setup.js generate one for you automatically.
# WARNING: Do not commit your real key. Keep it secret.
ENCRYPTION_KEY=""

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Optional: LLM Provider Keys (BYOK)
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# You can also configure API keys via the in-app Settings dialog.
# Keys added via the UI are encrypted at rest and never logged.
# The platform works without any of these — a free demo model (GLM-4.6)
# is available out of the box.

# OpenRouter (https://openrouter.ai/keys)
# OPENROUTER_API_KEY=""

# OpenAI (https://platform.openai.com/api-keys)
# OPENAI_API_KEY=""

# Anthropic (https://console.anthropic.com/settings/keys)
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=""

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Optional: Deployment Tokens
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Netlify personal access token for one-click deploys
# (https://app.netlify.com/user/applications#personal-access-tokens)
# NETLIFY_TOKEN=""
